> deduction paid in the following year to be taken in the current year.
>  However, income that is not from MA sources that is accumulated for
> charity or nonresident beneficiaries are not taxable at the trust level f=
or
> MA purposes.  The residual estate is divided as 10% to Joshua, 20% to
